Title: Iron Eagle IV
Actors: Louis Gossett Jr., Jason Cadieux, Joanne Vannicola, Max Piersig
Plot: While Chappy Sinclair is saddled with a bunch of misfits and delinquents for his flight school, he turns to his protégé Doug Masters to assist him in rounding the into shape for an important competition. During their training, they stumble upon a group of subversive air force officers who are dealing in toxic waste as a sideline.
